---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy & Disclaimer - Simple Senior Fitness"
  description="Read our privacy policy, medical disclaimer, and terms of use. Learn how we protect your data and the limitations of the wellness information we provide."
  keywords="privacy policy, disclaimer, terms of use, medical disclaimer, Simple Senior Fitness"
  canonicalUrl="https://yourdomain.com/privacy-policy"
  author="Simple Senior Fitness"
>
  <main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto pb-12 px-6">
    <section class="pt-10 pb-8 max-w-4xl">
      <span class="inline-block py-1.5 px-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-6">
        Privacy Policy & Disclaimer
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">
        Last updated: January 2025
      </p>
    </section>

    <article class="max-w-4xl space-y-8">

      <!-- Quick Navigation -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-surface-dark/50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">list</span>
          On This Page
        </h2>
        <nav>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#medical-disclaimer">Medical Disclaimer</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#information-collection">Information We Collect</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#cookies">Cookies & Tracking</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#third-party">Third-Party Services</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#your-rights">Your Rights</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline" href="#contact">Contact Information</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <!-- Medical Disclaimer -->
      <section id="medical-disclaimer">
        <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-3xl flex-shrink-0">warning</span>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-4">Medical Disclaimer</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                The content on Simple Senior Fitness is for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. It is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
                I am not a licensed physician, physical therapist, chiropractor, or healthcare provider. I am a regular person sharing my personal experiences with traditional Japanese wellness practices that have helped me with chronic pain.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
                <strong>Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified healthcare provider</strong> with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something you have read on this website.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
                If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your doctor or emergency services immediately. Simple Senior Fitness does not recommend or endorse any specific tests, physicians, products, procedures, opinions, or other information that may be mentioned on this site.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Exercise Disclaimer -->
      <section>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-3xl flex-shrink-0">fitness_center</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-3">Exercise & Physical Activity Disclaimer</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-3">
                The stretching techniques and exercises described on this website should be performed with caution. Before beginning any exercise program, including the Japanese wellness techniques discussed here, you should:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">•</span>
                  Consult with your healthcare provider, especially if you have any pre-existing conditions, injuries, or chronic pain
                </li>
                <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">•</span>
                  Stop immediately if you experience pain, dizziness, or discomfort
                </li>
                <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">•</span>
                  Understand that you perform these exercises at your own risk
                </li>
                <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">•</span>
                  Recognize that individual results may vary
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Privacy Policy -->
      <section id="privacy-policy">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4 mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          At Simple Senior Fitness, I respect your privacy and am committed to protecting any personal information you share with me. This privacy policy explains how I collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit this website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Information Collection -->
      <section id="information-collection">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-4">
          Information I Collect
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Automatically Collected Information</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">
              When you visit this website, certain information may be automatically collected, including your IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URLs, and pages viewed. This information is used to analyze trends, administer the site, and improve user experience.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Information You Provide</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">
              If you contact me through email or a contact form, I will collect the information you provide, such as your name and email address. This information is used solely to respond to your inquiry and is never sold to third parties.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cookies -->
      <section id="cookies">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-4">
          Cookies & Tracking Technologies
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small files stored on your device that help me understand how visitors use the site.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          <strong>Types of cookies used:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">•</span>
            <span><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function properly</span>
          </li>
          <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">•</span>
            <span><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Help me understand how visitors interact with the site</span>
          </li>
          <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">•</span>
            <span><strong>Preference cookies:</strong> Remember your settings, such as dark mode preference</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
          You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect your experience on this site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Third-Party Services -->
      <section id="third-party">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-4">
          Third-Party Services
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This website may use third-party services that collect information used to identify you. These services have their own privacy policies, and I encourage you to review them:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">•</span>
            <span><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website traffic analysis</span>
          </li>
          <li class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400">•</span>
            <span><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> For typography</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Your Rights -->
      <section id="your-rights">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-4">
          Your Rights
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark"><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark"><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark"><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark"><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing of your data</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mt-4">
          To exercise any of these rights, please contact me using the information below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Terms of Use -->
      <section id="terms-of-use">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-8 mb-4">
          Terms of Use
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          By accessing and using Simple Senior Fitness, you agree to the following terms:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Content Usage</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">All content on this site is for personal, non-commercial use. You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify content without permission.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Accuracy</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">While I strive to provide accurate information, I make no warranties about the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of the content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">External Links</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">This site may contain links to external websites. I am not responsible for the content or privacy practices of those sites.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Limitation of Liability</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Simple Senior Fitness shall not be held liable for any damages arising from the use of this website or reliance on its content.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Affiliate Disclosure -->
      <section>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark pt-8 mb-4">
          Affiliate Disclosure
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          This website may contain affiliate links, which means I may receive a commission if you click on a link and make a purchase. This comes at no additional cost to you. I only recommend products or services that I genuinely believe may be helpful.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
          Any affiliate relationships will be clearly disclosed on pages containing such links.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Changes to Policy -->
      <section>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark pt-8 mb-4">
          Changes to This Policy
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
          I may update this Privacy Policy and Disclaimer from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. I encourage you to review this page periodically for any changes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-8 mb-4">
          Contact Information
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the Disclaimer, or your personal data, please contact me:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <p class="text-base text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">
            <strong>Simple Senior Fitness</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">
            Email: contact@simpleseniorfitness.com
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Back to Home -->
      <div class="pt-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline font-medium">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_back</span>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>

    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
